test_presence_of_duplicates_in_result:
assert (2 == 3)
 +  where 2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x72b243e69bc0>([76])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x72b243e69bc0> = [[1], [1, 76], [76, 1], [76, 1, 76], [1], [1, 76], ...].count
test_if_sublist_product_equals_number:
assert 8 == 76
 +  where 8 = <built-in function prod>([2, 4])
 +    where <built-in function prod> = math.prod
